items.title: The Amon Carter Museum Flops in East-Meets-West Exhibition
items.description: It rambles, detours, and disserves the good art in the show, but there are so many wonders elsewhere in the museum.

items.title: In Such Times, We Need Law, Civil Discourse, and Normal Politics More Than Ever
items.description: The killing of Charlie Kirk will be a radicalizing moment but should not alter our commitment to the American Way.
